            "title": "The Architectural Metamorphosis of the Digital Frontier: A Comprehensive Analysis of Blockchain Evolution and the Web3 Paradigm",
            "subtitle": "From Centralized Web to Decentralized Ownership",
            "author": "Asrnova Team",
